			Profile
			
			Dr.Wang,MSc(awardedbyNanjingNormalUniversityin1993),Ph.D.(awardedbyNanjingUniversityin2000),isanAssociateProfessoratSchoolofEconomics,ZhejiangUniversity,Hangzhou,China.In1993hebecameacivilservantandsincethenhehadbeenworkingformorethan10yearsforJiangsuprovincialgovernmentattheProvincialDevelopmentandReformCommission,inNanjing(CapitalcityofJiangsuprovince).In2002hemovedtotheZhejiangUniversityandbecameateacherintheDepartmentofPublicAdministration,hehaslecturedincoursesofpublicpolicyanalysis,socialsecuritypolicies,macroeconomics,andprincipalsofeconomics,urbanandregionaleconomics,anddevelopmentstudiesaswell.In2005hemovedtotheDepartmentofEconomicsatSchoolofEconomics,ZhejiangUniversity.AndnowheisthedeputyheadoftheDepartmentofPublicFinanceatZhejiangUniversity.
&nbsp;
Dr.WangvisitedtheNorwegianSchoolofEconomicsandBusinessAdministration(NHH)inschoolyear1998/1999asavisitingScholar;inschoolyear2001/2002hevisitedtheMelbourneUniversityintheCentreforPublicPolicyasapostdoctoralfellow.HevisitedtheGlasgowUniversityintheDepartmentofEconomicsinspring2006andtheHertieSchoolofGovernanceinBerlininsummer2007asvisitingprofessor.HewasthevisitingprofessorinSchoolonLocalDevelopmentattheUniversityofTrento,Italy,inAutumn2008.HevisitedtotheBankofFinlandandtheUNUWIDERin2009,vistedtotheStaeUniversity-HigherSchoolofEconomicsinMoscowinApril2010.
			
				
